Homepage: https://www.kali.org/
Description: Kali NetHunter Rootless Edition CLI
 NetHunter CLI provides command-line access to Kali NetHunter tools
 and packages without requiring root access. Enables penetration
 testing and security tools through PRoot environment integration.
